Package maize

Interface Summary
Bot Interface for logic and stuffs
MazeFactory Interface for Maze generators
 

Class Summary
AdvancedBot This bot retains some state and performs more complex actions easily.
Agent Agent class which defines the API which bots access.
AgentFactory Agent factory for building Agents
CircleMazeFactory Creates an maze made of concentric cirlces
ClassSerializer Class for loading and saving Maze objects into files
DFSMazeFactory This factory produces mazes using the Depth First Search algorithm, albeit randomised.
Direction Helper class for directions
EmptyMazeFactory Creates an empty maze for the purposes of testing
FullDFSMazeFactory Creates a more twisty maze by using a fully random Depth First Search.
LineMazeFactory Creates an empty maze for the purposes of testing
Maze The Maze model.
Orientation Helper class for directions
RandomScatterMazeFactory Creates an maze made of random scattered bricks
ScatterMazeFactory Creates an maze made of scattered bricks
StateBot This bot is abstract and should be extended to create your own bots.
